escription/></item><item><title>Ethical Screening Policy</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-screening-policy/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 22:33:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-screening-policy/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Human Rights Policy</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/human-rights-policy/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 22:33:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/human-rights-policy/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Ethical Approach To Ai</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-approach-to-ai/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-approach-to-ai/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Ethical Policy</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-policy/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-policy/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Ethical Principles</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-principles/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical-principles/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Fraud And Corruption – Sustainable Business Alliance</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/fraud-and-corruption--sustainable-business-alliance/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/fraud-and-corruption--sustainable-business-alliance/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Human Rights</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/human-rights/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/human-rights/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="principle-one-human-rights">Principle One: Human Rights&lt;/h1>
&lt;h3 id="businesses-should-support-and-respect-the-protection-of-internationally-proclaimed-human-rights">Businesses should support and respect the protection of internationally proclaimed human rights.&lt;/h3>
&lt;h2 id="what-does-it-mean">What does it mean?&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>This Principle sets out the UN Global Compact’s overarching expectation of business on human rights, namely, to respect and support human rights. Respecting human rights means a business should use due diligence to avoid infringing human rights (“do no harm”) and should address adverse human rights impacts with which they are involved. In addition, beyond respecting human rights, business is encouraged to take action to support human rights. This means seeing the opportunity to take voluntary action to make a positive contribution towards the protection and fulfillment of human rights whether through core business,strategic social investment/philanthropy, public policy engagement/advocacy, and/or partnerships and other collective action. Action to support human rights should be a complement to and not a substitute for action to respect human rights. Special attention should be paid to the rights of vulnerable groups, including women, children, people with disabilities, indigenous peoples, migrant workers, older persons etc.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Modern Slavery And Human Trafficking Statement</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/modern-slavery-and-human-trafficking-statement/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/modern-slavery-and-human-trafficking-statement/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Modern Slavery Policies</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/modern-slavery-policies/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:06:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/modern-slavery-policies/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Ethical Decision Making</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical--decision-making/</link><pubDate>Sun, 27 Apr 2025 19:30:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/ethics/ethical--decision-making/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Ethics Focused Risk Assessment</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/e